For Windows : 

Installation : Take a look at this : https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/languages/cpp

Steps : 

1. Install C/C++ extensions
2. Install gcc/g++ Compiler
3. Save Environment Path variable with mingw install location : Generally it would be : C:\msys64\ucrt64\bin
4. create simple program and compile it with g++ programname.cpp and run with ./a.exe
